::Fenox/Iron Fist::

Fenox continues to fly above the water, carrying D and getting closer 
to the Iron Fist.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
The Iron Fists scans the waters again, getting a better reading on 
Prebon now. Debree was beginning to be washed away, making scanning 
easier.

Four plates open on the underside of the Iron Fist, four rods sliding 
out. Underwater defences were ready. As soon as Prebon would get into 
optimal range......
